Steven Schultz from Momentum chose Hammerson as his stock pick of the day. It is a JSE-listed European shopping centre owner. Late last year it announced its intention to take over Intu Properties, the former Liberty International portfolio. If the deal does go through, it will become the third-largest shopping centre owner in Europe. The company has proven to be effective at managing shopping centres through different economic cycles. OR LISTEN TO THE AUDIO: Listen to all latest podcasts here.